Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:33.61,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,My toes, hungry for a last chance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:36.83,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,Began to dance across the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:39.41,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,An ordinary stance will never enchant
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:42.94,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,Only stars can be the envy of jewels
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:46.43,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,Tears and sweat float on the surface, the traces of blood
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:49.64,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,To only swim in someone’s eyes is but a play
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:52.22,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,But the stage won’t let me go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.22,0:00:56.01,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,I’ll seek for it forevermore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:58.02,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,Longing for it
Comment: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:00.29,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,(I’ve never seen (oh) such a liar.)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:03.96,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,You must have been born with this level of depravity
Comment: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:07.84,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,(This lie is love. And this lie is a gift to the world.)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:10.52,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,Remember who you lived alongside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:14.97,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,I’ll risk my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.99,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,I’ll give my life to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:22.13,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,After all, you gave me time, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:27.76,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,Once I fulfill all my desires
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:29.76,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,Once I achieve them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.76,0:01:32.46,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,I want to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:35.28,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,So I wish upon a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:40.52,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,Come, children of the stars, sleep well
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:47.03,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,The light will not dim, if you’re the ones who shine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:54.00,CR_DefaultItalics,,0,0,0,,Come, children of the stars, sleep well
